  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates a novel mechanism where PSMD14 acts as a deubiquitinating enzyme that stabilizes HMMR through K63-linked deubiquitination, leading to dual activation of TGF-\u03b2/Smad and PI3K/AKT/mTOR pathways in lung adenocarcinoma.",
    "The combination therapy of Capzimin (PSMD14 inhibitor) with galunisertib (TGF-\u03b2 inhibitor) shows synergistic anti-tumor effects, suggesting a promising therapeutic strategy.",
    "PSMD14 expression serves as both a diagnostic biomarker (AUC = 0.898) and prognostic indicator across multiple survival metrics in LUAD patients."
  ]
